UserManager.ValueAccessLevel Resource access levels: - READ: user is allowed to read the resource - WRITE_LIMITED: user has READ access to the resource + limited write (no widgets) - WRITE_FULL: user has full access to the resource page (modulo widgets etc. that may be blocked)
